headline.print_headline: 3 Spanish Airmen Hurt in Djibouti Grenade Attack
headline.main: 3 Spanish Airmen Hurt in Djibouti Grenade Attack

lead_paragraph: Officials say three Spanish military airmen have been injured in a restaurant grenade attack in the tiny African country of Djibouti.
